OL,7,FPatel, 36, who now lives in Dubai but
OL,8,Fpreviously of Edstone Close, Bolton,
OL,9,Fwas found guilty of one count of
OL,10,Fconspiracy to commit police corruption.
OL,12,FKadir was given 15 months in prison
OL,13,Fand must also serve a one-year
OL,14,Fcommunity order on release.
OL,16,FPatel was handed a nine-month
OL,17,Fsuspended sentence and 120 hours of
OL,18,Funpaid community work. Two other men
OL,19,Fwere cleared of being involved in the
OL,20,Fscheme.
