OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Jennifer
OL,8,FAdams, GMP's Senior Investigating
OL,9,FOfficer for the investigation, said:
OL,10,F"Our investigations revealed that PC
OL,11,FKadir was in the Apex offices when he
OL,12,Fwas both on and off-duty, accessing
OL,13,Fconfidential police information from
OL,14,Fhis work mobile phone.
OL,16,F"The business obtained information
OL,17,Fthey were not entitled to, without
OL,18,Fredaction, much faster than a
OL,19,Fsolicitor could and without the fees a
OL,20,Fsolicitor would have to pay.
