OL,7,F"Apex would only be paid out if the
OL,8,Fclient was not at fault. Kadir's
OL,9,Fillegal activities meant they could
OL,10,Ffind that information out quickly and
OL,11,Fnot waste their time on clients who
OL,12,Fwould make them no money.
OL,14,F"The claims management company charged
OL,15,Finsurance companies #7,000 for four
OL,16,Fweeks' car hire and #1,400 for storage
OL,17,Fover the same period, so they were
OL,18,Fprofiting significantly.
