OL,7,F"Kadir received an array of benefits
OL,8,Fincluding car hire, car servicing,
OL,9,Fhospitality and loans from the co-
OL,10,Faccused.
OL,12,F"Our financial investigations also
OL,13,Fshowed that the officer had a gambling
OL,14,Fproblem."
