OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Jennifer
OL,8,FAdams, said: "This was a lengthy and
OL,9,Fdetailed investigation. The sentences
OL,10,Fhanded down by the court today are
OL,11,Ftestament to the diligence of the
OL,12,Fofficers in the Anti-Corruption Unit
OL,13,Fand sends a clear message from the
OL,14,Fjudiciary about the expectations it
OL,15,Fhas of serving police officers.
