OL,7,F"My officers tenaciously pursued all
OL,8,Flines of enquiry to expose the full
OL,9,Fextent of this criminality to achieve
OL,10,Fa successful prosecution in co-
OL,11,Foperation with our colleagues in the
OL,12,FSerious Crime Division of the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service.
OL,15,F"PC Kadir benefited personally from
OL,16,Fhis activities and exposed other
OL,17,Fmembers of the public to
OL,18,Funquantifiable risk by divulging
OL,19,Fsensitive personal information, which
OL,20,Fwe can show was shared more widely
OL,21,Famongst the community.
